{"tid":672650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 中大長鏈陣鎖33架GoBee Bike","createTime":"2018-05-21T07:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T09:44:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a0639b7a6771a2bf874c12d548d2330fc50fbb","tid":672650,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397187&d=JedxukupOXq29ZbJdMFYBG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4beb5c5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397187&h=d8f9f466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397187</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n中大長鏈陣鎖33架GoBee Bike<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/21ls5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F21ls5p6.jpg&h=34fd6b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中大用長鐵鏈將共享單車鎖埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學有人將幾十架共享單車上鎖「私有化」？讀者黃小姐稱她近日見到中文大學中大教研樓附近泊咗好多GoBee Bike喺度，佢諗住租嚟踩吓，點知去到時卻發現超過廿架共享單車俾人用鐵鏈額外上咗鎖，好似私有化咗咁，懷疑有人違規。<br />\n<br />\n小記上周五現場了解，喺中大香港生物科技研究院同中大教研樓對開，見到兩批共33架共享單車，發現除咗短鐵鏈同鎖頭，仲有長鐵鏈將鎖埋啲單車，冇幾遠豎咗個告示牌，提醒「此等GoBee Bike單車暫停使用，等候單車公司回收」。<br />\n<br />\n小記打去保安處問，原來近日唔少人喺中大亂泊共享單車，於是保安人員就「捉晒啲單車」，等單車公司派人攞番走。中大發言人亦話，近期校園有共享單車俾人隨意擺放嘅情況出現，對行人和道路使用者構成障礙及危險，並違反大學有關單車停泊規定。所以保安處只係跟規矩鎖車。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 蜘蛛叔飛躍10樓外牆整冷氣<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點●即聽"},{"pid":"b6b158b2419f03a7e4952b412736b467383c8271","tid":672650,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"共享經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbc2d03a3c8078630d3ac37ce6e082ca5a8c587","tid":672650,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"啲共享單車成日都周圍放，同違例泊車一樣，同又唔會俾警察抄牌，梗係無阻嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08da7fe98134eb1e04da2faefc20ba2571994b4","tid":672650,"uid":106247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"一早應該咁做啦<br />\n公共地方俾佢泊車做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef18f2370ae9e5efb290da86dc63c4b05a178674","tid":672650,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲共享單車成日都周圍放，同違例泊車一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">但</span>又唔會俾警察抄牌，梗係無阻嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff7e92d453ab09b6ee18120f21971a6407f21681","tid":672650,"uid":33635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4521b134b38300b0c31d2d6a380a94a9e23432","tid":672650,"uid":10064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"最好見一架鎖一架<br />\n用公家地做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2da31552db9a304c632526dc0382c82ee4d969","tid":672650,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"呢啲車鎖左成年有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22abe1bc179a7c74ad31f284e5b11df88e5f80e5","tid":672650,"uid":23531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實共享單車好事黎，佢個app有建議泊車位 唔會阻到人..係啲用家唔理周街泊先搞到咁..我見過有人用單車鎖鎖住部ofo係荃灣碼頭..9成係想長用 唔想比人揸走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢啲人真係自私到仆街"}